{
  "stem": "4247.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, I'm speaking figuratively, but very close to the truth, because there's no gas chambers in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The general attitude of my father, or the type of Jew he was, is that let's move.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We have to go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Pack up and let's go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Let's do what they tell us we must do, right?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So that's a sort of support, because that was your question, that was the mentality behind the support I was getting from my parents.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My mother was a-- a gentlewoman.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She had no-- no political stand, belief, right?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She cared for me, and that's where it all ended.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And aside from that systematic and bureaucratic signaling of anti-Semitism, did you see evidence of overt anti-Semitism at school amongst people you knew?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, absolutely.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very early in-- in-- in my elementary school, I remember it was a young bully there, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and it was, you know, on a popular level, on the-- on the-- on the level what became [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] became almost a slogan, right?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When he told me during the break in the schoolyard, something to the effect that you're a dirty Jew, I'm not quite sure what has provoked it and what were the circumstances, but I remember it very clearly.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I would have been eight or nine at the time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I just went there, and I-- I smacked him on the nose.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And his nose bleeded.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was the last-- the last time that he ever said that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was the-- that was the-- the early experience I had in-- in-- in these matters.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there was numerous clauses which excluded Jewish students to go to university.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Incidentally, these numerous clauses, for historical clarity, I would like to say, was enforced way back.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
